@page "/training-content"


    <style>
        /* Unique CSS Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ol {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        code {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

    img {
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

        footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>

    <div>
        <h1>Creating a New Training in PhishSims</h1>

        <ol>
            <li>
                <h2>Log in to Your PhishSims Account</h2>
                <p>Use your username and password to access your account.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Navigate to the "Training" Section</h2>
                <p>Locate and click on the "Training" section in the dashboard side-menu.</p>
            <img src="/img/Train1.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Click on the "New Training" Button</h2>
                <p>Within the "Training" section, find and click on the "New Training" button.</p>
            <img src="/img/Train2.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Enter a Descriptive Title</h2>
                <p>In the designated field, enter a clear and descriptive training name for your new training.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training6.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Provide a Training Trigger</h2>
                <p>Select Training Trigger as "YES" if you doesnot want to import recipants and select "NO" if you want to import recipants.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training7.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Select Appropriate Campaign</h2>
                <p>Select an appropriate campaign from the drop down.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training8.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training9.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
            <h2>Select Training Video for Training</h2>
                <p>Select the Training Video which you uploaded already form the drop down.</p>
            <p>For more information about How to upload Training Video, <a href="/training-video-content">click here</a>.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training10.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training11.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Select Training Quiz </h2>
                <p>Select the training Quiz for the training, So that after training user should attent the quiz.</p>
            <p>For more information about How to create Quiz for Training, <a href="/quiz-content">click here</a>.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training12.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training13.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Training Category</h2>
            <p>Slect the Training Category from the drop down.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training14.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training15.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>Click on the "Save" Button</h2>
                <p>Finalize the creation of your new training by clicking on the "Save" button and success popup will appear.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training1.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training16.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            </li>
        <li>
            <h2>Click on the "Publish" Button</h2>
            <p>Now, after saving the training, Click on Publish button to publis the Training and will get the success popup.</p>
            <img src="/img/Training2.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training18.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
        </li>
        <li>
            <h2>Modify Training</h2>
            <p>If you want to modify your training, you can click on "Modify" button on the "All Training" page where training data is available.</p>
            <img src="/img/Train3.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <p>After modifying your training click on "Save" and "Publish".</p>
            <img src="/img/Training17.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
            <img src="/img/Training18.png" alt="Screenshot of accessing campaign creation page">
        </li>
        </ol>

        <footer>&copy; 2024 PhishSims. All rights reserved.</footer>
    </div>

